<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Warning - Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdcb6e 0%, #e17055 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #fdcb6e;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .warning-box h3 {
            color: #d63031;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Important Account Notice</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name || 'there' %>,</h2>

            <p>We wanted to bring something important to your attention regarding your Engagematic account.</p>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>Action Required</h3>
                <p><strong>Issue:</strong> <%= warningReason || 'Payment method needs attention' %></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>What you need to do:</strong></p>
                <ul style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li><%= actionRequired || 'Please update your payment method to avoid service interruption' %></li>
                </ul>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #d63031;"><strong>If not resolved, your account may be suspended on: <%= deadlineDate || 'Within 7 days' %></strong></p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Why this matters:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Prevent service interruption</li>
                <li>Maintain uninterrupted access to all features</li>
                <li>Keep your content and data safe</li>
                <li>Avoid account suspension</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= actionUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    Resolve This Issue â†’
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you've already taken action, please ignore this email. If you need help, reply to this email and our support team will assist you immediately.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">We're here to help you maintain uninterrupted access to Engagematic!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

